{"tid":1162401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近排虧虧地，想大量入手神盾海狗，但而家仲買唔買好？","createTime":"2019-05-20T00:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T01:27:20.000Z","uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a481e42a0b70932f15fdcbf5cdba21bc20f74917","tid":1162401,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LZJJe8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LZJJe8.png&h=217bc72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許：我都有頭有面，有人識嘅&hellip;&hellip;點會咁大膽咁樣同人哋講呢啲嘢！<span style=\"color: red;\">更何況我有心無力！</span>早前石修先同我講，佢話網上有一段流言，話佢同老婆離婚，同助手有染，好離譜囉，我當然唔信，其實網絡上嘅嘢唔可以盡信，我覺得依家好似燒到埋嚟我度咁！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家我心大心細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aee46d1c12e3f57a8d75d45d13b5a2bcc6b0390","tid":1162401,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"食左有無用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1679c39ee2eb85876ff49efbb8e913b3d1bc55","tid":1162401,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"有無爸絲食過？"}]}